倍退你？</description></item><item><title>租房押金被扣了？房东敢扣你钱，你就敢让他吐出来</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%BC%E9%87%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%BC%E9%87%91/</guid><description>退房的时候房东找各种理由扣你押金——墙壁脏了、家电旧了、地板花了。哪些该你赔，哪些不该？律师说清楚。</description></item></channel></rss>